(Smith 1977:3), (Jones y Wilson 1971:Figura 2), (Johnson et al. 1970:Tabla 1), (Taylor 1964:23, 72-78), a Smith (1977:3), Jones y Wilson (1971:Figura 2), Johnson et al. (l970:Tabla 1) 
